OL,9,G0900 Four in a Bed
OL,10,     FThe competition kicks off at
OL,11,     FWharfe House in Wetherby with B&B
OL,12,     Fnewbie Pauline Cox, who has a full
OL,13,     Fhouse for the very first time. But
OL,14,     Fthe narrow antique beds are a
OL,15,     Fcause for concern.
OL,16,G0930 Four in a Bed
OL,17,     FThe second visit is to Wortwell
OL,18,     FHall Barn in Norfolk, where
OL,19,     Fhusband-and-wife team Jenny and
OL,20,     FClive Aylett strive for
OL,21,     Fperfection. But a kitchen meltdown
OL,22,     Fresults in a fundamental error.
